## A few notes on the design:

- "OPEN TO INTERNSHIPS" tag with a pulsing dot — a nod to the priority-tag pattern from Focus Flow, repurposed here as a status indicator.
- Bio in serif/warm sans, proof statement set in monospace like a terminal log — separates "what I say about myself" from "the evidence," visually.
- Email button ends in a blinking cursor — small signature touch, ties back to your engineering/terminal instinct without going full hacker-green-on-black cliché.
- Swap you@example.com for your real email before publishing.
